data.description: In-Town Convenience for this 3BR/2.5BA luxury villa in gated 55 & over community near downtown Clayton. For mtn. living at its finest, outdoor living features incl. an Eze-Breeze year-round screen enclosed porch, rear open deck & rocking-chair front porch.  Home has an open floor plan, kitchen w/ granite c-tops & stainless appliances, vaulted great room w/ stone fireplace, dining area & private office space. Spacious master suite incl. tray ceiling, luxurious dbl vanity bath & large closet w/ built-ins. 2 large guest bedrooms share a bath. A powder room & laundry complete the 1 level home. Attached 2 car garage w/ plenty of space. Amenities incl. a clubhouse w/ meeting space, exercise room, putting green, gated security & walking trails.
